title: Kawhi Leonard, Joel Embiid, Lakers, Warriors-Rockets, and Baker Mayfield
itunes:title: Kawhi Leonard, Joel Embiid, Lakers, Warriors-Rockets, and Baker Mayfield
description:
Colin discusses why Toronto Raptors F Kawhi Leonard isn't valuable, the continuing issues with Philadelphia 76ers C Joel Embiid, the dysfunction of the Los Angeles Lakers, the game 3 missed call in the Warriors-Rockets series, and his response to Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield. Guests include Howard Beck, Nate Robinson, Matt Barnes, and Oliver Luck.
